      "content": "These so-called progressive shifts are not mere policy disagreements; they are a direct assault on the moral foundations of our children. When we allow radical agendas to dictate what is right or wrong, we are handing our youth a confused and fractured worldview. We must reject this cultural erosion because it threatens to dismantle the very fabric of our future generations. It is time to defend our children by defending our values!",
      "source": "target",
